    skos:definition "Prepare & Present Market Problem Research Discovery business activity is in charge of reporting the discovery of the market problem research. <br/><br/>This business activity includes tasks that identify the users of the 'market problem report' and designs effective 'market problem communication information' to address expectations of answers to the 'market problem research discovery' insights.<br/>"@en ;
